      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0006",
      "text": "Establish Streaming (ESTS)",
      "bbox": [
        128.2,
        106.97,
        259.81,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0007",
      "text": "4.2.6.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        187.03,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0008",
      "text": "The ESTS ELS requests a temporary allocation of Credit known as Streaming Credit large enough to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        539.94,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0009",
      "text": "perform continuous streaming of Data frames.  The SOF of the ESTS Request identifies the class for",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        540.07,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0010",
      "text": "which Credit is being estimated. See FC-FS-2 for the usage of this frame.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        420.31,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0011",
      "text": "4.2.6.2  Protocol",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        172.6,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0012",
      "text": "a) Establish Streaming Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        226.96,
        299.1,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0013",
      "text": "b) LS_ACC or LS_RJT Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        250.96,
        287.89,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0014",
      "text": "4.2.6.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        221.54,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0015",
      "text": "Addressing:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        155.0,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0016",
      "text": " The S_ID field designates the source Nx_Port requesting Streaming.  The D_ID field",
      "bbox": [
        155.1,
        298.96,
        539.98,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0017",
      "text": "designates the destination Nx_Port addressed.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        303.19,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0018",
      "text": "Payload:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        137.66,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0019",
      "text": " The format of the Payload is shown in table 10.",
      "bbox": [
        137.64,
        334.96,
        348.67,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0020",
      "text": "4.2.6.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        209.29,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0021",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        138.19,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0022",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies rejection of the ESTS command",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        466.96,
        357.0,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0023",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        142.05,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0024",
      "text": "LS_ACC signifies successful completion of the ESTS function.  The format of the LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        490.96,
        540.08,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0025",
      "text": "Payload is shown in table 11.  The Payload shall contain Streaming Credit allocated in the Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.89,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0026",
      "text": "end-to-end Credit field of the appropriate Class Service Parameters (see 6.6.5).  The Class Validity",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        539.91,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0027",
      "text": "bit, when set to one, identifies the class that contains the Streaming Credit.  The recipient shall ignore",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        539.97,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p047_s0028",
      "text": "the other Service Parameter fields.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        249.85,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
